Congratulations, **you discovered one of the shortcomings of strategy pattern**:

&gt; The strategy pattern can be used to host different algorithms which either have no parameters or the set of parameters for each algorithm is the same. However, it falls short if various algorithms with different sets of parameters are to be used.

 **Luckily, this [paper](https://github.com/Sebastian-Nielsen/Strategy-Pattern-with-different-parameters/blob/master/paperThatPresentsTheSolution.pdf) presents an elegant solution:** 
