In 2017, this `MultipartAutoConfiguration` class was moved to `org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.web.servlet` package with commit [Restructure web auto-configuration](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/commit/b76ca0bf8f61aafe2f812911f208200c96c4bc69#diff-16a62b1030b7e79d6796fa945ae0a3e127437c3ee6e688e1e33b64f6c753c810)

```
- package org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.web;
+ package org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.web.servlet;
